name: SÌ NACRE EAU DE PARFUM 2020
description: Envelop yourself in radiance with Sì Nacre Eau de Parfum 2020, a glimmering version of the chypre Sì fragrance. For a limited time, Sì is transformed with a swirl of golden shimmer that leaves a pearlescent gleam on the skin. Just perfect for special occasions, or those moments when you just want to feel that little bit more luxurious.
